      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and represents the pinnacle of its model class. It has been meticulously maintained, with a flawless exterior finish and an interior that still looks and feels brand new. Every mechanical component has been serviced to the highest standard, ensuring a driving experience that is as smooth and reliable as the day it left the showroom. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for perfection.",
