      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest possible standards. This unit exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every surface remains unblemished, reflecting a history of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance. This is, without reservation, an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand perfection.",
