    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This S54-powered icon features a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the chassis remains taut with no subframe fatigue. Every bushing and suspension component is OEM+, ensuring precise turn-in and mechanical transparency. Rod bearings and VANOS have been addressed preventatively. This is a turn-key, investment-quality example for the discerning purist.",
